Package com.percussion.loader.ui

Interface Summary
IPSConfigChangeListener This interface specifies the listener interface to be implemented to receive configuration change events in the content loader UI.
IPSConfigPanel An interface that must be implemented from all editor panels written for the configuration dialog.
IPSExtractorConfigChangeListener This interface may be implemented by one of the sub-panels within a configuration panel of a extractor.
IPSExtractorConfigTabPanel An interface that must be implemented for all extractor config tab panels.
IPSUIPlugin A project known as Site Migration (see spec by Martin Genhart in spec db) includes a client for scanning and analyzing a set of resources to convert them to a set of Rx CMS items and then upload them to a Rhythmyx server.
 

Class Summary
PSAbstractExtractorConfigTabPanel Abstract class that provides default implementations of most methods in the IPSExtractorConfigTabPanel interface as well as other common methods for extractor config tab panel sub-classes.
PSConfigPanel The default implementation for the IPSConfigPanel interface.
PSExtractorConfigChangeEvent The event object passed around to extractor configuration change listeners.
PSExtractorConfigContext This class is used as the repository for the edited extractor definition.
PSExtractorConfigPanel This class can be used as the super class for the UI configuration panel for all extractor definitions.
PSItemExtractorConfigPanel A Panel that repesents an Item Extractor and may contain zero or more tab panels that represent different sections of the item extractor to be edited.
